name: Hipster Farnese
description:
An animation based on one of the real
marble statues by the artist Leo
Caillard. This statue is inspired by the
iconic ? Hercule Farnese ? statue
from ancient Greece. Leo Caillard
carves Sunglasses and Hat in marble
to make it familiar and connected to
the present. If the price of this NFT
reaches 6 eth : a real and unique
version of The ? Hipster Farnese ?
made in white statuary marble by Leo
Caillard will be available for the first
owner of this NFT !
